# CODEOWNERS
# Maps file patterns to the owner(s) whose review is REQUIRED on PRs that
# touch them (when "Require review from Code Owners" is enabled in the ruleset).
# The LAST matching pattern wins.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ---- Default owner for everything in the repo ----
*                       @shadeo5

# ---- Medium tier (informational owner; base 1-review still applies) ----
/src/                   @shadeo5

# ---- High tier: the repo's crown-jewel paths ----
# Changes here can alter infrastructure or the governance gates themselves,
# so they REQUIRE code-owner (your) approval specifically.
/infra/                 @shadeo5
/.github/               @shadeo5
/.github/workflows/     @shadeo5
/.github/CODEOWNERS      @shadeo5
